text: Masaba Gupta, Satyadeep Misra Are Expecting First Child: Two Little Feet Are On Their Way Fashion designer and actress Masaba Gupta took to Instagram to announce that she is expecting a child with her husband Satyadeep Misra. Fashion designer and actor Masaba Gupta recently took to Instagram to announce she expecting a child with her husband Satyadeep Misra. Friends and family react. Read to know more. Fashion designer-actress Masaba Gupta and Satyadeep Misra are gearing up to welcome a new addition to their family as they announced their pregnancy in an Instagram post on Thursday, April 18, evening. Masaba Gupta shared three images in a joint post with her husband, including one where the couple can be seen seated on the floor together. Masaba And Satyadeep Announce PregnancyFashion designer and actor Masaba Gupta and her husband recently took to Instagram to announce that they are expecting their first child. Along with a carousel of three pictures, they penned the caption, "In other news - Two little feet are on their way to us! Please send love, blessings and banana chips ( plain salted ONLY) #babyonboard #mom&dad." Related News Friends And Family ReactActress Parineeti Chopra was among the first to react to the post. Her comment read, "Congrats mama". Kareena Kapoor commented, "Congratulations best girl best momma to be and to dear Sattuuu too happy to hear this." Kriti Sanon said, "Congratulations," with two heart emojis. The newlyweds announced their union through a joint post on Instagram. Wedding photos showed Masaba and Satyadeep dressed in coordinating pink attire, commemorating their special day. And thanks for letting me pick the caption - this is gonna be great!" Masaba Gupta and Satyadeep Misra reportedly began their relationship in 2020 after meeting on the set of her show Masaba Masaba.
